theorem clopen_of_P1_closed {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hClosed : IsClosed (A : Set X)) (hP1 : Topology.P1 (A : Set X)) :
    IsOpen A ∧ IsClosed (A : Set X) := by
  -- Convert `P1` into `P3` using the closedness of `A`.
  have hP3 : Topology.P3 (A : Set X) :=
    (Topology.P1_iff_P3_of_closed (A := A) hClosed).1 hP1
  -- Turn `P3` into openness under the same closedness assumption.
  have hOpen : IsOpen (A : Set X) :=
    (Topology.P3_iff_open_of_closed (A := A) hClosed).1 hP3
  exact And.intro hOpen hClosed
